## __Rules:__

> **1.** SOTW will occur every two weeks (so voting can take place).
> **2.** SOTW will be announced and voted on in the announcements channel.
> **3.** Shredders must include the name of the shredder, technology included, all builders, etc.
> **4.** Only one angle can be used for the build, and it must be in the form of a (static) image. 
> **5.** Moderators and SOTW staff may intervene if the winning shredders are deemed "low-quality".


> Remember: Shredders are judged on aesthetics and technology.


## __Submission:__

> Send it in the SOTW channel or via tickets (if you want it to be private until voting).
> Must be a static image including: name of the shredder, technology included, all builders, etc.


## __Prizes:__

> **1st-3rd place**
> "SOTW winner" role + shredder featured on youtube (not guaranteed)
> Ability to apply for s++

> Rewards can be added at any time



